  <div class="container">
    <div class="row row-centered">

      <div class="largeheader">
        <h1>About Read&Eat</h1>
      </div>

    <div class="well">
      <p>
        Read&Eat is the go-to website for students who may have limited experience, income or free time, or other issues that hinder them from cooking proper meals in their daily life.</br></br>
        Read&Eat provides an oasis of tasty, varied and healthy (*cough* and unhealthy) food that is <b>cheap and easy</b> to make, submitted by students from all over the globe.</br></br>
        Tired of having the same boring slice of bread with ham every morning? Running out of creative dinner ideas for impressing your family and friends, but also don't want to kill your budget?</br></br>
        <b>Read&Eat gotcha covered!</b></br></br>
        Take a peek inside our ever-growing database of simple, cheap and delicious recipes made by students all over the world, and let your mind and stomach be inspired.</br>
        Maybe you even have some great suggestions that you'd like to share yourself? If so, <b>register today</b> and bring it out to the masses!</br></br>
        Happy cooking!
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>"Like" and "Comment" symbols by <a href="http://glyphicons.com/" >Glyphicons</a></p>

  </div>
</div>

